      "writtenOn": "2020-04-08T19:02:41Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Yeah, that\u0027s why I call the base class disconnect() last, which frees them. Not sure I see a problem with that, except fragility? We could provide a function to free fStagingBuffers in GrGpu, which would make it clearer/less fragile I suppose.",
